name: Stretch
description:
These shoes are easy to grab, easy to go, easy to wear! Each shoe is carefully assembled with a grip tight sole, making them perfect to travel and play both indoors and out, lined with fleece for strength and thickness, and made with a durable (and ADORABLE!) cotton outer. Each shoe has elastic in the heel to keep them on your feet, but it is thick enough elastic to ensure they don't pinch!

Sizes Available: 
0-3 months (Approx. 4") 
3-6 months (Approx. 4.5") 
6-12 months (Approx. 5") 
12-18 months (Approx. 5.5") 
18-24 months (Approx. 6") 
24-30 months (Approx. 6.5")

name: CUSTOM Blankets!
description:
The power of minky is amazing. Babies, toddlers, and kids all go crazy over this stuff! It's soft, fluffy, cuddly, and keeps our kids young! My 7 and 3 year old both love this stuff! 

Give someone the gift of love and snuggles with a CUSTOM baby blanket. All I need is a simple direction and together we can make something beautiful and unique. A gift that will last a life time! 

If you are into Star Wars, Disney Princess, Ninja Turtles, vintage fabrics, or just need help finding THE perfect blanket, I am your girl!  

Shop around Esty and other places, my prices can't be beat! These fabrics are expensive, but I do my best to keep prices fair by shopping SMART!! 

**Fabrics subject to availability

name: CUSTOM KICKS!
description:
This is what makes my job worth doing! Designing and daydreaming! So, here is the deal...

YOU DREAM IT, I DO IT!

Custom shoes are great baby shower gifts, great for birthday parties, for halloween, dress up, and so much more! Have that one baby item you can't STAND to part with? Upcycle them and turn them into shoes!! The possibilities are endless here, and I love a challenge, so bring it on! 

This custom price includes me shopping, specifically for your, and spending the extra time creatively to whip up your dreams. 

The turn around on custom orders varies based on if I need to order the fabric. If you have a deadline, please email me prior to purchase. Standard turnaround on these can be estimated at 3 weeks. Though I always do my best to meet any deadline! 

***Please leave sizes in notes to seller DURING PAYPAL CHECKOUT!! If your forget to do this, or can't figure out how email scrunchnose@yahoo.com with your sizes. ***
